comments: Brunson (NYK) is moving alongside Smith Jr.'s (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Finney-Smith (BKN) is retreating along Randle's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact as Smith Jr. (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball to steal it from Randle.
Randle (NYK) moves into and delivers contact to Smith Jr.'s (BKN) body, which dislodges Smith Jr. as he begins is dribble up the court.
Anunoby (NYK) moves forward into and initiates illegal contact with Bridges (BKN), which affects the shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) legally contests and cleanly blocks Brunson's (NYK) driving shot attempt.
Hart (NYK) legally contests and cleanly blocks Smith Jr.'s (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Achiuwa (NYK) legally deflects the ball away after Hart (NYK) cleanly blocked the shot before it made contact with the backboard and it no longer has a chance to score.
Anunoby (NYK) makes contact with the loose ball to deflect it away from Finney-Smith (BKN) and incidental follow-through contact occurs as their arms get briefly tangled.
Anunoby (NYK) legally contests and cleanly blocks Johnson's (BKN) shot attempt at the basket.
The ball remains in bounds before Hart (NYK) grabs the loose ball.
Anunoby (NYK) is moving alongside Bridges' (BKN) path with a resting forearm on his body as marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Bridges (BKN) gathers the ball on his right foot and establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he maintains prior to passing.
Claxton (BKN) jumps vertically and collapses one arm into his body and brings the other into a vertical position as he absorbs the incidental contact that occurs during Hart's (NYK) layup attempt.
Anunoby (NYK) and Claxton (BKN) mutually engage and quickly disengage with one another as marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in Anunoby's (NYK) path and slightly turns his body as he braces himself to absorb the ensuing contact during the pick.
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on Brunson (NYK).
A timeout is called and granted prior to Thomas' (BKN) pass that Anunoby (NYK) deflects away from Bridges (BKN).
Hart's (NYK) right hand brushes Bridges' (BKN) left shoulder and marginal contact occurs as Bridges makes his intended pass.
Achiuwa (NYK) legally contests Johnson's (BKN) jump shot attempt. Anunoby (NYK) avoids making contact with Johnson after he releases the shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) initiates contact with Randle's (NYK) arm/shoulder as he reaches for the ball on the steal attempt.
Hart (NYK) legally contests Bridges' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
